"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/c5_UL3P-LB6Zq9xYLkq8x.jpg?height=1268&width=2255)\\n\\n### Hello, DAOist community, past and future sponsors. There are exciting times on the horizon! Here’s all that The DAOist fam should be aware of and schedule for!\\n\\n**Sponsorship perks and prices are the same for all events and the same as The DAOist Lisbon:**\\n\\n\\\\[TOP\\\\] Patron Level: 12k\\n\\n\\\\[MID\\\\] Ride or DAO: 6.5k\\n\\n\\\\[LOW\\\\] Sister DAO: 2.5k\\n\\n*COUNTERPARTS VARY FOR EACH EVENT AND ARE AT THE DISCRETION OF ORGANISING GROUPS - MAKE SURE TO CHECK EACH EVENT PAGE.*\\n\\n### Upcoming event dates:\\n\\n* **[The DAOist’s Valentine](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-s-Valentine-10c4733adf48466a8dea99334663710c)** | Denver | 14th of February 2022 |\\n* **[The DAOist’s Ciudad de México](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-Mexico-a150ad97cee14d13918da79e955d19c8)** | Mexico | 2nd & 3rd of March 2022 | Lead: [Chuy Garcia](https://t.me/chuygarcia92)\\n* **[The DAOist’s Barcelona](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-Barcelona-035fc1d8f41d4797a3a5c7f264ca2408)** | April 2022 | Lead: [Jahed Durruti](https://t.me/jahed_momand)\\n* **[The Global Governance Gathering (The DAOist +++)](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-GGG-91d0893ea42442c686aa3dec25dc3598)** | 18th-19th of April 2022 | Lead: [Felipe Duarte](https://t.me/Elementarycomplexity)\\n\\n*All contacts on telegram.*\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4fzIx2dMRDZfCMcO0LNON.png?height=632&width=1754)\\n\\n### Denver | The DAOist’s Valentine | 14th of February 2022\\n\\nThe community will gather to share their love for DAO’s right before EthDenver. This will be the first decentralized The DAOist organized by an independent team - thank god they are also makers of MCON and long-time friends of DAOs!\\n\\nIf you’re coming to Denver and need to have DAO love straight to the heart\\n\\n**[Apply to give a talk, sponsor, or volunteer here.](https://kolektivo.notion.site/The-DAOist-s-Valentine-10c4733adf48466a8dea99334663710c)**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ZA6S8YqiVOu5J34XU_5QS.png?height=590&width=1712)\\n\\n### The DAOist - Mexico City - 2nd & 3rd of March 2022\\n\\nLead: Chuy Garcia → [@chuygarcia92](https://t.me/chuygarcia92)\\n\\nThe DAOist Mexico will be mainly focused on bringing DAO culture to the local communities. An entire event designed for the locals, with talks in Spanish, sharing art and knowledge from DAOverse with one of the biggest capitals of the western world.\\n\\nWant to add to this hot mix?\\n\\n**[Apply to give a talk, sponsor, or volunteer here.](https://kolektivo.notion.site/The-DAOist-Mexico-a150ad97cee14d13918da79e955d19c8)**\\n\\n### The DAOist - Barcelona - April 2022\\n\\nLead: Jahed Durruti → [@jahed_momand](https://t.me/jahed_momand)\\n\\nRiding the coattails of the first [EthBCN](https://ethbarcelona.com/), this is our chance to activate one of the most cooperative-minded regions in the world and turn them on to DAOs. Barcelona is high up in the line to host a DAOist Embassy, also led by Jahed, a long-time pioneer of platform coops and we look forward to this event very much. ([Hi, Giveth!](https://giveth.io/))\\n\\n**[Apply to give a talk, sponsor, or volunteer here.](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-Barcelona-035fc1d8f41d4797a3a5c7f264ca2408)**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/s4ROYkA1V2kIekHkAIoX_.png?height=378&width=1308)\\n\\n### The Global Governance Gathering - 18-19th of April 2022\\n\\nLead: Felipe Duarte → [@Elementarycomplexity](https://t.me/Elementarycomplexity)\\n\\nThis will be a different “The DAOist”. The first day will be dedicated to manifesting intentional coordination between DAOs and will be attendant only by DAOists and they will be provided with all the comfort to get to kno and create together. The second day will be open to the public as usual.\\n\\nOur premise is that optimizing governance intimacy will require some meatspace facetime! Let’s get it!\\n\\n**[Apply, Sponsor, or Volunteer here.](https://www.notion.so/kolektivo/The-DAOist-GGG-91d0893ea42442c686aa3dec25dc3598)**\\n\\n**Don’t know what “the DAOist” is? [Click here to feel the vibe!](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U5aUHWDU7jg)**\",\"timestamp\":1640034863,\"title\":\"\\nUpcoming “The DAOist” Events (Q1 2022) - All you need to know!\\n\",\"publication\":\"thedaoist\"},\"digest\":\"2y5mUMg7ULt29253rc_8LMKtblVrmyXFk1lg3yTHDpw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0F3347b37F40870c68a7348B5660DFe37D357dba\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eEdMjmtB7jmyrajRiXS8tsWm-rYPUElC1NTeeEFExUc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fdgGbEhGUYUOatHwmUmSJnkrX0S2ghcIBw_7ogI7qiw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"H2CQpzPRlX5cfmwCTW79cYDnOI9moDj-55-pJhhZrl6yxF9Wtm81k7I3VjlBG-_KzeVKwL1uGSvit1JEsR2b0A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1f7f34375a7093b300487a1cb512013bf1309e47b355fafccad55fc89762dd957c3434b43118ac74e0aee0a189961fcb71c2eced79daa5d2a9cc19caf3b1673d1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on thedaoist.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eEdMjmtB7jmyrajRiXS8tsWm-rYPUElC1NTeeEFExUc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fdgGbEhGUYUOatHwmUmSJnkrX0S2ghcIBw_7ogI7qiw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Z7Ki6-AS98Pr0_91dZlROXUbUqYdRWhWY7ccdinGFFw\"}"